Alpha Online Banking este o aplicatie prietenoasa care iti ofera servicii bancare complete de oriunde in lume si oricand, simplu si rapid.

De ce sa folosesti aplicatia? Pentru ca ai banca la indemana, oricand si de oriunde, vezi cati bani ai in conturi, platesti facturi, schimbi valuta sau afli unde este cea mai apropiata sucursala Alpha Bank. 

Cu aplicatia de Alpha Online Banking te bucuri de: 
	•	un design nou, fresh si prietenos;
	•	ai control de la distanta asupra contului tau: poti inclusiv sa iti resetezi parola fara sa mai vii la banca;
	•	vezi cati bani ai in conturi si ce tranzactii ai efectuat;
	•	faci plati rapid si usor oriunde in lume;
	•	ai acces in orice moment la informatii despre creditele tale si planul de rambursare;
	•	platesti facturile la peste 100 de furnizori de utilitati, utilizand formularele dedicate;
	•	faci schimburi valutare rapid;
	•	alimentezi cardul de credit;
	•	constitui si lichidezi depozite;
	•	iti deschizi conturi noi, fara drumuri la banca;
	•	afli unde este cel mai apropiat ATM sau cea mai apropiata sucursala Alpha Bank.

Acum stii totul despre aplicatia Alpha Online Banking.  Incearc-o si tu!

Pentru mai multe informatii vizitati site-ul www.alphabank.ro

Alpha Online Banking is a user-friendly application that offers you complete banking services, from anywhere in the world and anytime, easy and quickly.

Why use the app? Because you have the bank at your fingerprints, anytime and anywhere – you can check your accounts’ balances, pay bills, exchange foreign currency or find out where the nearest Alpha Bank branch is.

Here are some of the benefits you can enjoy with the Alpha Online Banking application:
	•	a new, fresh and friendly design;
	•	remote control over your account: you can even reset your password without a visit to the branch;
	•	check your account balance and see your transactions;
	•	make fast and easy payments, anywhere in the world;
	•	access  your loans information and reimbursenment plan at any time;
	•	pay bills to over 100 utilities providers, using dedicated templates;
	•	quickly exchange currency;
	•	recharge your credit card;
	•	initiate and redeem deposits;
	•	open new bank accounts, without visits to the branch;
	•	find out where the nearest cash machine (ATM) or the nearest Alpha Bank branch is.

Now you know everything about the Alpha Online Banking application. Try it for yourself!

For more information please visit www.alphabank.ro

